# Feature: As a player I want to explore

Given I enter the dungeon
When I go north
Then I arrive in the next room to the north

Given I enter the dungeon
When I go east
Then I arrive in the next room to the east

Given I enter the dungeon
When I go west
Then I can't go that way

Given I enter the dungeon
When I go south
Then I can't go that way

Given I am in the room to the north of beginning room
When I go south
Then I arrive in the beginning room

Given I am in the room to the east of beginning room
When I go west
Then I arrive in the beginning room

Given I am in any room
When I type exit and hit enter
Then I exit the game
